properties.name: parameters
properties.value: { "noteText" : "You, who have found this temple...\n\nYou now stand in the Temple of Awakening. In ages past, young Nightar warriors tested their mettle within these halls. If you would seek to prove yourself, enter further into these halls, but know you shall be waylaid if you do. Should you survive, greater strength awaits within." }

properties.name: parameters
properties.value: { "noteText" : "This altar was crafted using the shattered pieces of the legendary sword, ^#e272d;Noxcalibur^reset;. It was said that when our first ruler emerged to lead us out of the shadows, he did so by cleaving away the darkness using that very blade. Throughout our history, our swordsmiths have produced numerous blades for upcoming warriors. Yet, every so often, warriors emerge with a sword that resonates with the altars. If yours is one such blade, consider this the mark of a new journey as you travel the great expanse as a ^#1e272d;Nightblessed^reset;." }

properties.name: parameters
properties.value: { "noteText" : "Upon this altar rests ^orange;a key^reset;. In our early days, we discovered that there are dimensions that lie beyond the boundaries of the known universe. If you dare to venture into that world, take heed: this world beyond worlds will test you. Lingering spirits of long-departed beings throughout the universe will waylay you." }
